Package: adjoin
Title: Constructing Adjacency Matrices Based on Spatial and Feature Similarity
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bradley R.", "Buchsbaum", email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1108-4866"))
Description: A collection of functions for constructing adjacency matrices based on spatial and feature-based similarity between data points. The package provides various methods to create spatial and feature-weighted adjacency matrices, enabling users to analyze and visualize complex data relationships.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
